amarnath ( kannada : ಅಮರ ನಾಥ ) is a 1978 indian kannada film , directed by k. mani murugan and produced by n. k. narayan , v. k. ramesh and p. b. walke .   the film stars ambarish , sundar krishna urs , dheerendra gopal and k. s. ashwath in lead roles .   the film had musical score by vijaya bhaskar .